WEBVTT

00:04:59.615 --> 00:05:02.687
Between now and 2050,

00:05:02.711 --> 00:05:09.600
when the global population
is set to move from today's 7.6 billion

00:05:09.624 --> 00:05:14.710
to tomorrow's 9.8 billion people,

00:05:14.734 --> 00:05:17.996
hundreds of millions of people

00:05:18.020 --> 00:05:22.977
will experience security, health
and safety issues.

00:05:25.127 --> 00:05:29.681
Imagine if you can
not feeling secure in your home --